<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.ecologicalsolutions.com.au/crystalwaters/history/buildings.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ecologicalsolutions.com.au/crystalwaters/history/buildings.html" rel="nofollow">Crystal Waters Village</a></li>
